sellerCard.description:
At Code Capital, we have experience and the expertise to help small, medium, and corporate-level businesses build a strong online presence and attract their dream customer base with our uniquely effective, innovative Web Design & Development services.

Using our creative minds, years of technical capabilities, and passion for applying top-notch UI/UX practices, we specialize in offering a complete end-to-end solution – from wireframes to the final product and everything in between. We've helped create dozens of tailored software solutions to date, and we can't wait to do the same for you.

description.content:
Important! Please contact me before placing the order!

I will develop any website for you, website with databases, mysql, queries, php.

I can make customer website according to your requirements, can create custom shops/carts functionality.

I will also customize your website, solve all kind of web related issues and errors.

Also do all kind of java scripting, php programming.


My expertise are in

  • PHP
  • javascript
  • jquery
  • SQL
  • Node.js
  • MongoDb
  • xampp
  • web Domain/hosting
  • web scraping/crawling


Let's Discuss your project and get it up and running! :)

Feel Free to contact. Quality is assured, satisfaction is guaranteed.
